            <title>[HBASE-13794] Add RegionLoad.getStorefiles(Bytes[] family)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-13794</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;RegionLoad already has getStorefiles but it might be very useful to get this information per column familly instead of per region only.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
